                  "hidden": false,
                  "description": "Specify the name of the migration project. For ABP applications after v4.4.0, the default value is '*.EntityFrameworkCore.csproj'; For ABP applications before v4.4.0, the default value is '*.EntityFrameworkCore.DbMigrations.csproj'; For ABP modules, the default value is '*.HttpApi.Host.csproj'. For example: --migration-project-name *.Web.Unified.csproj, abphelper will search '*.Web.Unified.csproj' file and make it as the migration project.",
